<li>CueR is the sixth member of the MerR family that responds to metal ions , the others being MerR itself ( Foster and Brown , 1985 ; Lund et al. , 1986 ) , PbrR ( B. Borremans , D. van der Lelie , J. L. Hobman and N. L. Brown , unpublished data ) , PMTR ( Noll et al. , 1998 ) , ZntR ( Brocklehurst et al. , 1999 ) and CoaR ( Rutherford et al. , 1999 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=11136469" target="_blank">11136469</a>]<br></li>
